data.description: Look at this beautiful new listing with amazing curb appeal! This home offers 4 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms and sits on almost 1/2 acre just outside of city limits. Walk through the foyer to the main level which features an oversized living room, kitchen, dining room, laundry area, 1/2 bath & the master bedroom. The kitchen offers granite countertops, custom cabinets & all major appliances are included. Take a stroll up the wide staircase to the upper level where more 3 bedrooms & the full bathroom are located. Don't forget to check out the fenced in backyard & the oversized garage. As a bonus the seller is offering a home warranty for the buyer! Call to schedule your appointment today!
